data.description: This beautiful home has recently undergone several updates, including a new storm door, professional air duct and vent cleaning, fresh paint, and new washer and dryer. Other desirable features include a wood-burning fireplace, refrigerator, designated car port, in a quiet, gated community. The home has been impeccably maintained by its current owner. Other updates include granite counter tops, cabinets, and flooring. Additionally, the home features a new furnace and a lovely patio. The community itself offers many amenities, such as a gym, pool, club house, mail room, snow removal, and partial utilities.
